## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives or recent developments in EHR technology. The variability in EHR systems and their implementation across different healthcare settings can lead to differing impacts on documentation time. Additionally, the studies reviewed may have limitations in sample size or methodology that could affect the generalizability of the results.

